  "body": "<p>The July kits are available now at <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a>. I really enjoyed working with these colors and fun elements. This month I got the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">main scrapbook kit</a>, the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/jennifer?aff=6cc2c70f\">Jennifer Add-on</a>, the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-project-life-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Project Life kit</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/winona?aff=6cc2c70f\">Winona</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762125563-2MJSJXMIXV5V0RW57KKZ/20a-lets_do_this-439x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20b-yes-555x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762147889-AZJD5LG3Q36YFQVPYMFE/20b-yes-555x600.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"20c-maddie_on_things-555x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762148021-ZMYDIV0P3527MPNZJE3X/20c-maddie_on_things-555x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20d-love_my_job-562x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762148399-KD8IQOQIKF0H7QIE72DO/20d-love_my_job-562x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20e-lisbon-554x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762148645-ZV5E9IKT30SLQJUI947P/20e-lisbon-554x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20f-home-554x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762149377-SATIEUZQ3SK9VHJ5HUJC/20f-home-554x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20g-going_places_with_you-564x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762149708-IGTU40OEX5BJH4BOJ9BM/20g-going_places_with_you-564x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>We designed an exclusive stamp set for the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Scrapbook kit</a>. It's the only place you can get it! Shop for all the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico Valley High kits</a> and check out all the creative team work <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/valley-high/scrapbook?aff=6cc2c70f\">here</a>.</p><p>SPECIAL OFFER! NEW SUBSCRIBERS can get $5 off each kit by using the following codes:</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Valley High scrapbook subscription</a>:  SCRAPBOOKVALLEY</p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-card-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Valley High card subscription</a>:  CARDVALLEY</p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-project-life-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Valley High Project Life subscription</a>:  PLVALLEY</p></li></ul><p>But hurry, coupon codes expire June 30th at midnight EST.</p><p>******************************************************************</p><p>For my layout using the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/valley-high-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Scrapbook Main kit only</a>, I thought I would show you how it came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20h-DSC_04141-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762228428-1QR4VEUBRK180Q07FQ5N/20h-DSC_04141-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20i-DSC_0415-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762228562-0OUAOL6EJY0F7AGHAAAT/20i-DSC_0415-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20j-DSC_04161-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762228828-5SEFJBF1UCRYCRM305N1/20j-DSC_04161-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20k-DSC_0417-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762229028-JQ161P1E9CVI37DUIS6Z/20k-DSC_0417-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20l-DSC_04181-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762229211-BURGEEVDKD68HSX3UDOG/20l-DSC_04181-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20m-DSC_0419-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762229823-UXI8F1MZETHF5ZCW0HFW/20m-DSC_0419-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20n-DSC_04201-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762230397-KVSFF7O5A29CMMMMXW6F/20n-DSC_04201-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20o-DSC_0421-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762230679-BGPN8PT9232ELFABC93W/20o-DSC_0421-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20p-25_weeks-552x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599762231262-91DBZ7GDQFNO6AKN95PF/20p-25_weeks-552x600.jpg\"/>"
